<div class="m-heading-1 border-green m-bordered">
    <h3>Clipboard JS</h3>
    <p>
        To initialize ClipboardJS, first add the wrapper class <code>.mt-clipboard-container</code> to your wrapper element and then add the class <code>.mt-clipboard</code> to any element needed to be copied. The Copy button will need
        a target reference <code>data-clipboard-target</code> to identify which element it will be copying.
        <br> For more info please check out
        <a href="https://clipboardjs.com/" target="_blank">the official documentation</a>.
    </p>
